## Realtime Broadcast (Sprint B — PC sala anon)

```sql
-- Funzione SECURITY DEFINER chiamata da trigger
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION public.broadcast_room_state_change()
RETURNS trigger
LANGUAGE plpgsql
SECURITY DEFINER
SET search_path = public, extensions
AS $$
BEGIN
  PERFORM realtime.send(
    jsonb_build_object('roomId', NEW.room_id, 'eventId', NEW.event_id),
    'room_state_changed',
    'room:' || NEW.room_id::text,
    false  -- private=false: chiunque conosca il topic puo' leggere (UUID v4 non enumerable)
  );
  RETURN NEW;
EXCEPTION WHEN OTHERS THEN
  -- non bloccare scritture applicative se Realtime e' giu'
  RETURN NEW;
END;
$$;

CREATE TRIGGER broadcast_room_state_change_trg
AFTER UPDATE ON public.room_state
FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION public.broadcast_room_state_change();
```

Topic `room:<uuid>` non enumerable (UUID v4 = 122 bit entropia). Comunicato al client SOLO dopo validazione `device_token` via Edge Function `room-player-bootstrap`.

