```sql
public.check_storage_quota()    -- BEFORE INSERT su presentation_versions
public.update_storage_used()    -- AFTER UPDATE su presentation_versions (status='ready')
public.check_events_quota()     -- BEFORE INSERT su events
public.check_rooms_quota()      -- BEFORE INSERT su rooms
public.current_tenant_suspended() -- SECURITY DEFINER, usato in policy RLS
```

## Edge Functions Deno — pattern sicuro

```typescript
// supabase/functions/<name>/index.ts
import { createClient } from 'jsr:@supabase/supabase-js@2';

Deno.serve(async (req) => {
  // CORS
  if (req.method === 'OPTIONS') {
    return new Response(null, { status: 204, headers: corsHeaders });
  }

  try {
    const authHeader = req.headers.get('Authorization');
    if (!authHeader) return jsonError(401, 'unauthorized');

    const supabase = createClient(
      Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_URL')!,
      Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_ANON_KEY')!,
      { global: { headers: { Authorization: authHeader } } },
    );

    const {
      data: { user },
    } = await supabase.auth.getUser();
    if (!user) return jsonError(401, 'unauthorized');

    const tenantId = user.app_metadata?.tenant_id;
    if (!tenantId) return jsonError(403, 'no_tenant');

    // ... logica scoped per tenantId
    return new Response(JSON.stringify({ ok: true }), {
      status: 200,
      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', ...corsHeaders },
    });
  } catch (err) {
    return jsonError(500, 'internal_error');
  }
});
```

**Edge Functions con `verify_jwt = false`** (in `supabase/config.toml`) — autenticano via token custom invece di JWT Supabase:

| Function                  | Token          | Verifica                                            |
| ------------------------- | -------------- | --------------------------------------------------- |
| `pair-claim`              | codice 6 cifre | `pairing_codes.code` non scaduto + non consumed     |
| `room-player-bootstrap`   | `device_token` | sha256 hex contro `paired_devices.pair_token_hash`  |
| `room-player-rename`      | `device_token` | idem                                                |
| `room-player-set-current` | `device_token` | idem + check presentation appartiene a stessa room  |
| `team-invite-accept`      | `invite_token` | `team_invitations.invite_token` non scaduto + valid |
| `cleanup-expired-codes`   | nessuno (cron) | DELETE `pairing_codes` scaduti — service role       |

**SECURITY DEFINER RPC chiamabili SOLO da Edge Function (mai da client):** `GRANT EXECUTE ON FUNCTION ... TO service_role` (no `authenticated`/`anon`). Esempio: `rpc_room_player_set_current` (Sprint I, autentica `device_token` e fa cross-room check anti-tampering).

